textDisplay: What it is about: A new "officially sponsored" military-religious hybrid temple opens in putin's russia, at the opening ceremony ( 0:56-1:17 ) one can see banners glorifying the former Soviet Union aggressive wars against Finland and the Baltic countries, ( 0:56-1:17 ) one can see closely standing huge numbers of russian troops without masks amid covid-19 around the world, the stairs are made from WWII captured German "trophy" military equipment (so in shoigu's words the people would step on the defeated enemies), and the mosaics originally featured stalin, putin, shoigu themselves with a slogan "Crimea is ours (krym nash)" (2:05-2:25) but eventually putin got scared of the backlash before elections and said to temporary remove these images in hope the "grateful" people will later ask for them  to be re-instated (3:05-3:15); the structure violated RF constitution on the separation of church and state, the funds were partly from forced "donations", there is a backlash against the structure, which exclusively devoted to glorify the past imperial victories of Russia/former Soviets, actual or intended, including the colonial occupation wars,
